snippet.title: BS F-Zero Grand Prix (Satellaview) - Knight League [60fps]
snippet.description:
Playlist: (https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLy6U_MlIBjvJRf3VaMZ9kllmcGCdFr9xw)

Complete gameplay of BS F-Zero Grand Prix - Knight League for the Satellaview.
The Satellaview was an adapter exclusive for the Super Famicom, it was only released in Japan, in its content you could download games and play them in a specific day time.

These games don't work very well in emulators, because the majority of emulators lacks of the Satellaview adapter, which means the games could be corrupted, this can be fixed with a patch, regardless this patch lets you play the game, it still contains a record ghost car glitch.
In these games it weren't supposed to be any music, but the patch put the music back on.

(Visit bszelda.zeldalegends.net/fzero.shtml for more information about the patches)

Watch in 60fps for a better visual quality.
